Detailed Description

Common Nomadik Multiprocessing Framework limits definition.

This file contains the limit definitions used into NMF.

Warning:
Don't modify it since it is also hardcoded in tools

Define Documentation

#define MAX_ATTRIBUTE_NAME_LENGTH   32

Maximum attribute name length.

Define the maximum attribute name length allowed by NMF.

#define MAX_COMMUNICATION_FIFO_SIZE   256

Maximum fifo size allowed for binding component.

Define the maximum fifo size allowed for binding component allowed by NMF when calling CM_BindComponentFromHost and CM_BindComponentAsynchronous.
